{{rfc|This text is in no section}}
Pinoy is a nickname a Pilipino gives his fellow countryman. 
Noypi is a backwards version of that name but again by a Pilipino.

A flip is a derogatory term and should never be considered anything other. It was coined by American Soldiers during WW2.  It doesnt mean fine or funny it means fucking little island person.

Young Pinoys have loosely used FLIP to describe their ethnic background. A more plausible origin of the term comes from the word Filipino. ''Italic text''

